# Local-only environment for non-Codespaces `devcontainer up` runs.
# Copy to `.devcontainer/devcontainer.env` (gitignored) and fill in the values you need.
#
# In GitHub Codespaces, DO NOT use this file — set these as Codespaces secrets
# (Settings → Codespaces → Secrets). They are injected automatically there.

# GitHub PAT for cross-repo git/gh auth (post-create runs `gh auth login --with-token`).
# PERSONAL_PAT=ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Dotfiles repo applied via chezmoi at create time (user/repo or a git URL).
# DOTFILES_REPO=emsilva/dotfiles

# Override the container timezone (default: America/Sao_Paulo).
# DEVCONTAINER_TZ=America/Los_Angeles
